    * **Right Part (Tower):** Four orange cylindrical blocks (index 12) form the four legs. Two yellow rectangular blocks (index 11) are placed horizontally on top of these legs, forming a platform. Another orange cylindrical block (index 12) sits on this platform, and finally, a yellow half-cylinder block (index 14) tops the structure.

**3. Determine the Assembly Order:**

A reasonable assembly order, ensuring stability, would be:
